    'portfolio.bio.about': 'Summary',
    'portfolio.bio.summary': 'R&D engineer who turns unclear requirements into loop-based automation systems, MCP/WebMCP tools, product platforms, and working software/hardware processes.',
    'portfolio.bio.details': 'As part of [RND-PRO](https://rnd-pro.com/), I design automation systems and the reusable tooling behind them: Agent Portal and MCP/WebMCP infrastructure, Symbiote Workspace / UI / Engine / Node, Web/PWA interfaces, lifecycle messaging platforms, media workflows, and hardware-backed systems such as ComplexScan, BoothBot, and AUTOBOX v1.\n\nR&D is the shared method across these projects, not one isolated job category. Earlier work spans 360 media platforms, personally developed JavaScript/Espruino control software after MEGAVISOR, server infrastructure, physical process automation, commercial production, export, bottle-catalog capture automation, and 3D production workflows.',
